    "description": "<strong>MULTIPLAYER CAR CHASE</strong>. You work for an electricity company, and you have been sent to retrieve the <i>Covex19 Crystal</i>. You must battle 9 other drivers in a <strong>fast paced, action packed</strong> Battle Royale, involving car chases and gun-combat in order to <u>extract the crystal</u> for your company.<br><br>You can:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Customise your characterCustomise weaponsShoot at carsDestroy carsCrash CarsWin engaging, physics-based car chasesSend in HelicoptersForm and break alliancesand ultimately, <strong>be the last one standing</strong></ul><br>The game uses simcade handling for the cars. Each car can be <strong>destroyed</strong> <i>piece by piece</i>, breaking off doors, smashing glass and snapping wheels!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124100/extras/9a07cd7bd31c173b778a6ea0eaac9bc9.poster.avif?t=1735001163\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124100/extras/9a07cd7bd31c173b778a6ea0eaac9bc9.webm?t=1735001163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124100/extras/9a07cd7bd31c173b778a6ea0eaac9bc9.mp4?t=1735001163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
